## Comment appeler un workflow n8n

Utilise l'outil `web_fetch` pour envoyer une requete POST au webhook n8n :

```
POST {{ n8n_webhook_base_url }}/webhook/<path>
Headers:
  Content-Type: application/json
  X-Webhook-Secret: ${N8N_WEBHOOK_SECRET}
Body:
  {
    "task": "description de la tache",
    "input": "donnees d'entree",
    "model": "claude-haiku",
    "callback_agent": "<ton agent id>"
  }
```

## Format de reponse attendu

```json
{
  "status": "success|error",
  "result": "...",
  "tokens_used": 0,
  "model_used": "..."
}
```

